query:
WITH new_resource AS (INSERT INTO resource (
                                                        id,
                                                        created_date_time,
                                                        modification_date_time,
                                                        resource_name,
                                                        ven_id,
                                                        attributes,
                                                        targets
                )
                VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), now(), now(), $1, $2, $3, $4)
                RETURNING
                    id,
                    created_date_time,
                    modification_date_time,
                    resource_name,
                    ven_id,
                    attributes,
                    targets as "targets:Vec<Target>")
            SELECT new_resource.*, v.client_id
            FROM new_resource
                     JOIN ven v ON v.id = new_resource.ven_id;
